end-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["currencyservice-0", "paymentservice-2", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-2", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "cartservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-07T00:10:23Z to 2025-06-07T00:29:23Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-07 00:10:23+00:00 to 2025-06-07 00:29:23+00:00"}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "cartservice-2", "paymentservice-1", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["currencyservice-0", "paymentservice-2", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-2", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "cartservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "node_cpu_usage_rate", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于日志数据分析，我发现了明确的故障模式。让我分析这些日志并提取关键信息。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"stress\", \"Byteman\", \"Agent failed to start\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\", \"StressHelper\", \"Transformer\", \"TriggerThread\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman stress注入故障导致Agent启动失败和重复加载异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Agent failed to start!, Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once, Exception in thread \\\"Attach Listener\\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 分析要点：\n\n1. **明确的故障模式识别**：\n   - 所有错误日志都来自 `adservice` 服务的三个实例（adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2）\n   - 出现了明显的 `stress` 注入相关错误，表明这是Chaos Mesh的故障注入实验\n\n2. **关键错误关键词**：\n   - `stress`：表明是压力测试相关的故障注入\n   - `Byteman`：Java字节码操作工具，用于故障注入\n   - `Agent failed to start`：Byteman代理启动失败\n   - `InvocationTargetException`：Java反射调用异常\n   - `attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`：重复加载代理错误\n\n3. **故障根因分析**：\n   - 这是Chaos Mesh对adservice进行的stress注入实验\n   - Byteman代理在加载过程中出现重复加载和启动失败的问题\n   - 故障涉及所有三个adservice实例，表明是系统性的故障注入问题\n\n4. **证据支持**：\n   - 所有三个节点上的adservice实例都出现了相同的错误模式\n   - 错误日志中明确提到了`AdService--stress-1749255024`这个stress规则\n   - 出现了`Agent failed to start!`和重复加载异常，表明故障注入执行失败", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的调用链数据，我现在可以分析这个故障的根因。让我仔细分析这些异常调用关系。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService/GetAds调用延迟从正常5.5秒增加到30-38秒，延迟倍数5.4-6.9倍，影响所有frontend实例，出现38次异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis HGET操作延迟从正常1.5秒增加到35.2秒，延迟倍数22.7倍；HMSET操作延迟从正常1.3秒增加到12.3秒，延迟倍数9.1倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmptyCart操作延迟从正常2.2-2.4秒增加到8.1-14.6秒，延迟倍数3.4-6.0倍；GetCart操作延迟从正常2.5秒增加到12.6秒，延迟倍数4.9倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**主要发现**：\n1. **AdService是主要根因**：所有frontend实例的AdService调用都出现严重延迟，延迟倍数高达6.9倍，影响范围最广\n2. **Redis存储层问题**：Redis操作延迟异常严重，HGET延迟倍数22.7倍，表明存储层存在性能瓶颈\n3. **CartService受影响**：由于依赖Redis，CartService的延迟也显著增加\n\n**根因分析**：\n- **AdService** 可能是故障的起始点，因为它影响所有前端实例\n- **Redis** 的性能问题可能加剧了CartService的延迟\n- 调用链显示：frontend → adservice 和 checkoutservice → cartservice → redis 都存在严重延迟\n\n建议优先排查AdService和Redis集群的健康状态。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于采集到的指标数据，我现在可以分析故障的根本原因。让我仔细分析这些异常指标：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存和CPU资源严重不足，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes下降35.87%，node_cpu_usage_rate上升20.76%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从12.54GB下降到8.73GB，node_cpu_usage_rate从34.23%上升到42.16%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"所有adservice实例的pod_cpu_usage显著上升，同时rrt和rrt_max指标出现严重性能退化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"adservice-0: pod_cpu_usage从0.01上升到0.6(193.44%)，rrt从3438ms上升到13924ms(120.79%)；adservice-1: pod_cpu_usage从0.0上升到0.6(200%)，rrt_max从43046ms上升到86549ms(67.14%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1, cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice实例出现高client_error_ratio和error_ratio，p99错误率分别达到18.22%和15.87%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-1: client_error_ratio p99从0%上升到18.22%；cartservice-2: error_ratio p99从0%上升到15.87%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **主要根因**：`aiops-k8s-08`节点出现严重资源瓶颈，内存可用量下降35.87%，CPU使用率上升20.76%，导致该节点上的服务性能严重退化。\n\n2. **关键发现**：\n   - `aiops-k8s-08`节点承载了多个关键服务（redis-cart-0、adservice-2、cartservice-1/2等）\n   - `adservice`所有实例都出现严重的CPU使用率上升和响应时间恶化\n   - `cartservice`出现高错误率，表明服务不可用或响应超时\n\n3. **故障传播路径**：节点资源不足 → adservice性能下降 → cartservice错误率上升 → 整体服务链受影响\n\n4. **建议**：需要检查`aiops-k8s-08`节点的具体资源使用情况，并考虑将部分负载迁移到其他节点以缓解压力。"}
